com.interpss.core.aclf.flow

Interface FlowInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FlowInterfaceImpl

    public interface FlowInterface
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'Interface'. flow interface defined for limit violation checking

    The following features are supported:

    • Network
    • On Peak Limit
    • Off Peak Limit
    • Interface Branches
    See Also:
    FlowInterfacePackage.getFlowInterface()
